21:27Z","closed_at":null,"author_association":"OWNER","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"1. 容器元素闭合标签前添加额外元素并设置`clear: both`\r\n2. 父元素触发块级格式化上下文(见块级可视化上下文部分)\r\n3. 设置容器元素伪元素进行清理[推荐的清理浮动方法](http://nicolasgallagher.com/micro-clearfix-hack/)\r\n\r\n```\r\n/**\r\n* 在标准浏览器下使用\r\n* 1 content内容为空格用于修复opera下文档中出现\r\n*   contenteditable属性时在清理浮动元素上下的空白\r\n* 2 使用display使用table而不是block：可以防止容器和\r\n*   子元素top-margin折叠,这样能使清理效果与BFC，IE6/7\r\n*   zoom: 1;一致\r\n**/\r\n\r\n.clearfix:before,\r\n.clearfix:after {\r\n    content: \" \"; /* 1 */\r\n    display: table; /* 2 */\r\n}\r\n\r\n.clearfix:after {\r\n    clear: both;\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n* IE 6/7下使用\r\n* 通过触发hasLayout实现包含浮动\r\n**/\r\n.clearfix {\r\n    *zoom: 1;\r\n}\r\n```","closed_by":null,"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/hankliu62.github.com/issues/131/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/hankliu62.github.com/issues/131/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null},"menus":[]},"__N_SSG":true}